1. *Bismo* mogli da odemo u kino. (We could go to the movies.)
2. Ja *bismo* bila radosna da ti pomognem. (I would be happy to help you.)
3. Oni *bisme* morali da napuste zemlju. (They had to leave the country.)
4. *Bismo* li mogli da razgovaramo o tome? (Could we talk about it?)
